The demolition or removal of
any of the following —
(a) a single house;
(b) an ancillary dwelling;
(c) an outbuilding;
(d) an external fixture;
(e) a boundary wall or
fence;
(f) a patio;
(g) a pergola;
(h) a verandah;
(i) a deck;
(j) a garage;
(k) a carport;
(l) a swimming pool;
(m) shade sails.

The erection or installation
of, or alterations or additions
to, any of the following on
the same lot as a single house
or a grouped dwelling —
(a) an ancillary dwelling;
(b) an outbuilding;
(c) an external fixture;
(d) a boundary wall or
fence;
(e) a patio;
(f) a pergola;
(g) a verandah;
(h) a deck;
(i) a garage;
(j) a carport.

Works that are urgently
necessary for any of the
following —
(a) public safety;
(b) the safety or security
of plant or equipment;
(c) the maintenance of
essential services;
(d) the protection of the
environment.
